'If I die then I will fight the Gods in heaven and the demons in hell, the King's words I believe those were.'
I say confidently.She scoffs and a expression of anger starts to manifest on her gorgeous face.' Then the
Queen's words were, If I do not have a heart then I will make one If I do not have a soul then I will take
one.' 'How dare you taint the sacred words of the Holy King and Queen with your filthy lies, I will end you for your
insolence you irreverent scum.Reka occidere eum!' she exclaims, infuriated by my deception.The snake transforms
into a terrifying serpent with menacing red eyes then in one bite takes me into it's mouth and swallows me whole.